00:34:36.679 --> 00:34:42.760
Danas stable coin je upravo uh krči put

00:34:39.879 --> 00:34:46.679
kriptu. Uh m uh mnogi najavljuju da će

00:34:42.760 --> 00:34:48.480
ih koristiti, mnogi najavljuju da će m

00:34:46.679 --> 00:34:52.399
